    <h2 class="page-header">How We Operate</h2>
    <p>
        All the teachings at Pikes Peak Vajra Vidya are free of charge, although donations to help support the monks and pay the rent and utilities
        are greatly appreciated.  Donations to the teachers are tax-deductible, but those to support the expenses of the sangha are not at this time, sorry.
    </p>
    <p>
        We aim to help and inspire each other as peers and colleagues.  If you have questions or need help we hope you will feel free to ask anyone, likewise
        that you will share sincerely without concern about credentials or doctrinal landmines.  The one writing this didn't go through "official channels" to get these
        remarks approved (at the moment at least there are none) but he hopes he has faithfully captured a little of the essential spirit of this sangha without
